    <releases>
      <release version="1.1.0" date="2020-04-08">
        <description>
          <p>New</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Added support for row cloning.</li>
            <li>Added support for superscript and subscript text formatting.</li>
            <li>Added support for using input methods to add text to rows and notes.</li>
            <li>Added selection submenu to contextual menu.</li>
            <li>Added new row selection commands: top, bottom, first child, previous sibling. next sibling, page up and page down.</li>
            <li>Added support for moving selected rows via keyboard shortcuts.</li>
            <li>Added ability to position the selected row at the top of the window.</li>
            <li>Added ability to delete the previous or next word via Control-Backspace/Delete keyboard shortcut.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Changes</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Improved readability of text formatting bar.</li>
            <li>Removed support for <em>m</em> command in selection traversal.</li>
            <li>Version number now output to .outliner file.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Bug Fixes</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Made metadata translatable (Thanks to Nathan Bonnemains).</li>
            <li>Fixed screenshot URLs in metadata.</li>
            <li>Fixed application crash when using the <em>a</em> command when top-level row is selected.</li>
            <li>Fixed node showing/hiding.</li>
          </ul>
        </description>
      </release>
